FBIS4-60132 "drnes099_d_94001" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 Libya Al-Qadhdhafi Cancels 'Id Ceremonies Over Yemen Al-Qadhdhafi Cancels 'Id Ceremonies Over Yemen LD2105131794 Tripoli Great Jamahiriyah Radio Network in Arabic 1230 GMT 21 May 94 LD2105131794 Tripoli Great Jamahiriyah Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpts] In protest against and as a mark of mourning for the secession of South Yemen that was announced last night, the brother leader of the revolution cancelled his decision to lead the 'Id prayers and deliver the sermon for the masses of worshippers who came to perform the 'Id al-Adha prayers. The remaining 'Id ceremonies are also cancelled. [passage omitted] This announcement came as the Arab masses in Libya and throughout the Arab world were preparing to mark the fourth anniversary of the declaration of unity in brotherly Yemen [words indistinct]. [passage omitted]
